Question: Explain how to reach your home without using any street names
Answer:
my home is very near to the middle school. when you drive to the school, before entering the main gate, turn right, then take the second turn when you see a pet store on your right hand. drive for about two minutes, you will see a big oak tree, turn left as soon as you see it. on your right hand side, there is a house decorated by twincle lights, that is my house.